	<dl>
	<dt>As an expatriate UK Citizen I'm disenfranchised...</dt>
	<dd><p>As an expatriate UK Citizen I'm disenfranchised. <br />I know no-one in the constituency I used to live in, and I can't register to vote at my parents' address. <br /></p>
	<small>
	written 6th May 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1862">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
